org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT gpx_files.id AS alias_0, gpx_files.id FROM gpx_files INNER JOIN gpx_file_tags ON gpx_file_tags.gpx_id = gpx_files.id LEFT OUTER JOIN users ON users.id = gpx_files.user_id WHERE gpx_files.visibility IN ("$1", "$2") AND gpx_file_tags.tag = "$3" AND gpx_files.visible = "$4" ORDER BY gpx_files.id DESC LIMIT "$5" OFFSET "$6"
